data.description: Bacon Crest Subdivision beauty! **New roof will be included, buyer has time to pick shingle color! Come check out this 4/3/2 plus basement! As you walk through the spacious entry way you are welcomed by the special ceilings and open concept living room. The large kitchen area is complimented by an island/breakfast bar and large pantry. The master bedroom offers plenty of space along with bathroom suite, double vanity's and a large walk-in closet with special storage. Did we mention the basement?! This could be used as an extra living space. Special items include granite countertops throughout, oversized garage and beautiful landscape.
